{"tid":159390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將羞辱當成教育因為訓練小孩未來接受強權的羞辱","createTime":"2017-03-17T03:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T06:55:05.000Z","uid":30807,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f161abba6b2555d915795e18b38f4bd037aa34","tid":159390,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"將羞辱當成教育, 是因為我們是訓練小孩, 未來也要接受各種強權的羞辱, 然後心甘情願, 認苦認命, 笑臉迎人, 甚至隨之起舞, 指鹿為馬. 心照不宣.<br />\n<br />\n來源：鄭立<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10155034951347357&amp;id=656167356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10155034951347357%26id%3D656167356&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=33710d99\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10155034951347357&amp;id=656167356</a>"},{"pid":"d781bd67359f4948a700cd6c0098528f5b2a86a3","tid":159390,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"同埋教中文，好多時都係教你揣摸上意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n議論文就係搵後生仔黎屌<br />\n又吹奏下d老不死"},{"pid":"aee4eb3f74d487a56fbeeaede7aa503895b5d6a8","tid":159390,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e228ed15197f7f8ad5b49ca02757543f3956c634","tid":159390,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"唔止咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓練員有絕對權力, 肆意羞辱學生, 即係間接話俾學生知有權力就可以為所欲為, 冇權力就任人魚肉<br />\n<br />\n信哂呢套諗法嘅話, 第時出到社會, 就會為咗得到權力不擇手段, 上咗位就好似當年訓練營嗰陣折磨無權力嘅人 (最仆街嘅係佢哋好多時唔係搵返羞辱佢哋嘅人報仇, 而係虐待無辜嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n呢種情況亦係構成家庭暴力循環嘅一大因素, 細路俾家長虐待 (肉體or精神), 長大之後角色轉換虐待返自己啲細路<br />\n<br />\n如果將呢種人際關係放大到社會, 係咪有啲似曾相識, 好似某種昆蟲嘅心態?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加埋&quot;(支)國民&quot;教育, 我有理由懷疑呢啲所謂訓練營嘅目的係將香港下一代支殘化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64cd0db9342a9f8544fa8eab98d59df66f51172","tid":159390,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔止咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓練員有絕對權力, 肆意羞辱學生, 即係間接話俾學生知有權力就可以為所欲為, 冇權力就任人魚肉<br />\n<br />\n信哂呢套諗法嘅話, 第時出到社會, 就會為咗得到權力不擇手段, 上咗位就好似當年訓練營嗰陣折磨無權力嘅人 (最仆街嘅係佢哋好多時唔係搵返羞辱佢哋嘅人報仇, 而係虐待無辜嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n呢種情況亦係構成家庭暴力循環嘅一大因素, 細路俾家長虐待 (肉體or精神), 長大之後角色轉換虐待返自己啲細路<br />\n<br />\n如果將呢種人際關係放大到社會, 係咪有啲似曾相識, 好似某種昆蟲嘅心態?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加埋&quot;(支)國民&quot;教育, 我有理由懷疑呢啲所謂訓練營嘅目的係將香港下一代支殘化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5ddf9c7e67d7c68a5859fc64da72985644bac9","tid":159390,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:58:14.000Z","msg":"我認為相反喎，對強權更加痛恨，播下革命種子。"},{"pid":"f818a6f3b4c954f4ac4c9372c00b680d8552d06d","tid":159390,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T05:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我認為相反喎，對強權更加痛恨，播下革命種子。</blockquote><br />\n有反抗意既人可能因此奮起<br />\n但亦有不少人就此被烙下奴隸的印"},{"pid":"4f6710e514ff9976d22cf75635c789c7fa799165","tid":159390,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T05:18:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/03/16/milgram-experiment/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2Fmilgram-experiment%2F&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7c46a562\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/03/16/milgram-experiment/</a><br />\n今朝睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b25ec65ebd84236e6d94291fadb8a9c2f94a46","tid":159390,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"一早講左係支那統戰手段"},{"pid":"d48c460b873cc027b28b1fa5ae762f66d8818274","tid":159390,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/03/16/milgram-experiment/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2Fmilgram-experiment%2F&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7c46a562\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cup.com.hk/2017/03/16/milgram-experiment/</a><br />\n今朝睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我幼稚園至小學係一間非正式補習社渡過<br />\n因為父母返工時間長，係補習社時間長過屋企<br />\n又係一個服從權威，做埋D違反良心既地方<br />\n包括一個人錯就罰其他人，同埋要你互罰&hellip;&hellip;"}]}